<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
We can solve this question using Two Approaches. (Here I have explained all the possible solutions of this problem).

1. Solved using Dynamic Programming Approach(Tabulation: Bottom Up) With 2D Array(output) Extra Space.
2. Solved using Dynamic Programming Approach(Tabulation: Bottom Up) With 1D Array(output) Extra Space.

# Approach
